caption:
Do you take time throughout the day to recalibrate to regroup to refuel? 

If you don’t, you’re doing yourself a disservice. 

You’ve got lunch take lunch get out of the office get some air, go for a walk. 

God forbid something happens to you, you know, there may be some quiet time. Who knows how long? 

But your position will be posted and they will be looking for a replacement. 

Best believe that, you can’t help anybody without your body. So take care of the one that you have.
